---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import placeholderImg from '../assets/images/placeholder.jpg';
---
<section id="portfolio" class="py-32 px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 md:gap-24 items-center">
    <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mb-12">The Vision</h2>
      <div class="font-sans text-text-secondary space-y-8 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        <p>
          I approach photography not just as a means of capturing light, but as a way of preserving the raw, unpolished essence of a moment. Every space, every interaction, and every shadow tells a story that deserves to be documented with integrity.
        </p>
        <p>
          Focusing on both documentary and architectural photography, my goal is to frame the unspoken narratives of Oklahoma. By emphasizing extreme minimalism and a high-contrast monochrome aesthetic, the subjects are allowed to speak for themselves without the distraction of unnecessary elements.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
      <Image src={placeholderImg} alt="Photographer" class="w-full aspect-[3/4] object-cover" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>